How to make quizzes with Backbone.

Types of quizzes
- Multiple choice
-- Intro text or image, a question, and possible answers

- Question & Answer
-- Intro text or image, a question, and an input for answering

Models
- Account
-- current_question

- Question
-- intro_text - String - intro text or image (html)
-- question - String - the question
-- choices - Object - possible answers, if multiple choice
-- answer - String, Number - user's answer

Collections
- Questions

Views
- QuestionView
- ProgressView
- App

File Structure
- project_name/
-- app_name/
--- scripts/
--- styles/
--- images/
